a state appeals court thursday threw out the 
theftbyextortion conviction of former congressman and mecham 
administration aide sam steiger saying political armtwisting 
doesnt constitute an illegal act 
in a 30 ruling the midlevel court of appeals said it did not 
approve of steigers conduct but feared it could have a chilling 
