party i might have something similar to say he said 
baker and shevardnardze are spending the weekend in jackson hole 
wyo discussing arms control and other ussoviet issues 
now will we conclude a treaty in wyoming the answer to that 
is obviously no baker said i think if you will judge us at the 
end of the day hopefully next sunday that you will agree that 
weve moved the process forward substantially across the full range 
of our arms control agenda 
