about one third are expected to seek restitution with the total 
return between 25 million and 50 million 
itt also will pay 105 million to establish consumer protection 
trust funds 867 million in civil penalties and 575000 for legal 
costs and a tollfree phone number for consumers claiming refunds 
van de kamp said itt took advantage of people in desperate need 
of money and charged up to 35 percent interest on loans and 
attached items 
